{"tid":1587656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到文宣組見到］文宣新方向","createTime":"2019-09-22T13:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T17:31:15.000Z","uid":16946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9688fa4b62833eae123647f2316f6e9ae34776d1","tid":1587656,"uid":16946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:23:23.000Z","msg":"依家嘅文宣大部份係黑警/藍絲罪證或者口號類型嘅宣傳<br />\n<br />\n呢啲文宣的確可以鞏固我方立場同拉攏民意 吸引咗好多上年紀嘅人睇<br />\n<br />\n但事到如今 <span style=\"color: red;\">大部份人立場已定</span><br />\n咁成功拉攏咗更多人入我地陣營之後 應該點做？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">心態變黃之後下一步就係行動都要變黃！<br />\n令佢地變成我地嘅行動力！</span><br />\n<br />\n好多上咗年紀嘅 即使係深黃 都好少可會上前線 佢地有時想幫都唔知可以做啲咩<br />\n所以要<span style=\"color: red;\">進一步幫佢地令抗爭融入生活</span><br />\n<br />\n行動文宣黎講 除咗現有嘅週末行動嘅文宣外 我地可以加多啲<span style=\"color: gold;\">指南/教學類型嘅文宣</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>指南類：</strong></span></span><br />\n- 罷食list<br />\n- 罷買list<br />\n- 美心旗下商鋪list<br />\n- 港鐵商場list<br />\n- TVB廣告商list <br />\netc<br />\n總之所有要抵制嘅 都大大力宣傳 可以貼喺連儂牆或者商場 等佢地喺日常生活都可以增加我方嘅bargaining power<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">教學類：</span></strong></span><br />\n- 如何用Twitter retweet對我方有利嘅資訊<br />\n可參考：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M91YYH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM91YYH6.jpg&h=cc871b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 如何用Reddit/Quora留言<br />\n- 如何用Facebook喺TVB廣告商派嬲同留言<br />\n可參考此fb page：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBg6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=fcd8b70e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\n<br />\n總之所有網戰嘅參軍方法 都可以整啲簡單教學<br />\n(香港人好少用tweeter reddit呢類大型外國網站 <span style=\"color: red;\">主要都淨係喺ig story同fb度post文宣</span> 所以即使係做比同溫層嘅都好有用)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">未開twitter reddit quora accout嘅巴絲快啲開返個！</span>國際戰線係大量五毛！<br />\n仲有929就係全球抗共大遊行 呢幾日大家快啲上twitter reddit煲煲佢！<br />\n<br />\n最後想講<br />\n唔好以為有其他人做緊你就唔洗做 <span style=\"color: red;\">每一條戰線都需要人幫手 大家儘量做得幾多得幾多</span> 唔好睇少自己一分力 二百萬人一人一啖口水都浸撚死班黑警<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nUseful Links:<br />\nTwitter軍tg group<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBg6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=4af2cac7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n抵制TVB廣告商fb group<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBg6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=fcd8b70e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a>"},{"pid":"b33b74fd673e4cb8585d179449ec3021e729c89c","tid":1587656,"uid":16946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:23:38.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f736c5f65d7afe33fbaa66d7b9d862e1d66d7f2a","tid":1587656,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12e5331ec9bfd334b16afe5684aaf479da92bbae","tid":1587656,"uid":16946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7ddc2b335f19441cf3015ce061eab2e37ac608e9","tid":1587656,"uid":16946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"24cce1735774d64ce4a174ff67868db384e75b9c","tid":1587656,"uid":16946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7b14984b58ab289dbd1f5989b158bccd93f14fff","tid":1587656,"uid":16946,"like":0,